.TH AES 2
.SH NAME
setupAESstate, aesCBCencrypt, aesCBCdecrypt, setupAESXCBCstate, aesXCBCmac, setupAESGCMstate - advanced encryption standard (rijndael)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <u.h>
.br
.B #include <libc.h>
.br
.B #include <mp.h>
.br
.B #include <libsec.h>
